### ========================================================
### LAB | JPA Relationships and Inheritance
### request.http - Test File
### ========================================================

### --------------------------------------------------------
### MODULE 1: Public Relations Contact System
### --------------------------------------------------------
### Contact entities created:
### - Name (Embeddable): salutation, firstName, middleName, lastName
### - Contact (Entity): id, company, title, embedded Name
### --------------------------------------------------------

GET http://localhost:8080/api/contacts
Accept: application/json

### Expected: List of 4 contacts with embedded Name objects

---

### --------------------------------------------------------
### MODULE 2: Nurse Association Division Management
### --------------------------------------------------------
### Entities created:
### - Association: id, name, list of divisions
### - Division: id, name, district, president (Member), list of members
### - Member: id, name, status (ACTIVE/LAPSED), renewalDate
### --------------------------------------------------------

GET http://localhost:8080/api/associations
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 1 Association with 7 Divisions, each with >= 1 Member

GET http://localhost:8080/api/divisions/district/us-east-1%20%28N.%20Virginia%29
Accept: application/json

### Expected: Division(s) in the specified district

GET http://localhost:8080/api/members
Accept: application/json

### Expected: List of all members

---

### --------------------------------------------------------
### MODULE 3: Event Management System
### --------------------------------------------------------
### Entities created:
### - Event (Parent with @Inheritance JOINED): id, title, date, duration, location, list of guests
### - Conference (extends Event): list of speakers
### - Exhibition (extends Event)
### - Guest: id, name, status (ATTENDING/NOT_ATTENDING/NO_RESPONSE), event
### - Speaker: id, name, presentationDuration, conference
### --------------------------------------------------------

GET http://localhost:8080/api/events
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 3 Events (1 Event, 1 Conference, 1 Exhibition)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/conferences
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 1 Conference with speakers list

GET http://localhost:8080/api/exhibitions
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 1 Exhibition

GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests/status/ATTENDING
Accept: application/json

### Expected: Guests with ATTENDING status

GET http://localhost:8080/api/speakers
Accept: application/json

### Expected: List of speakers linked to Conference

---

### --------------------------------------------------------
### OPTIONAL: Task Management System
### --------------------------------------------------------
### Entities created:
### - Task (Parent with @Inheritance SINGLE_TABLE): id, title, dueDate, completed
### - BillableTask: hourlyRate (BigDecimal)
### - InternalTask: no additional fields
### --------------------------------------------------------

GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 3 Tasks (1 InternalTask, 2 BillableTask)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 2 BillableTasks with hourlyRate

GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/internal
Accept: application/json

### Expected: 1 InternalTask

---

### ========================================================
### JPA RELATIONSHIPS VERIFIED:
### ========================================================
### 1. @Embedded - Name inside Contact
### 2. @OneToMany - Association -> Divisions
### 3. @ManyToOne - Division -> Association
### 4. @OneToOne - Division -> President (Member)
### 5. @OneToMany - Division -> Members
### 6. @ManyToOne - Member -> Division
### 7. @Inheritance(JOINED) - Event -> Conference, Exhibition
### 8. @OneToMany - Event -> Guests
### 9. @ManyToOne - Guest -> Event
### 10. @OneToMany - Conference -> Speakers
### 11. @ManyToOne - Speaker -> Conference
### 12. @Inheritance(SINGLE_TABLE) - Task -> BillableTask, InternalTask
### ========================================================
